content.text: entities = [ KnowledgeEntity("2 + 2 = 4", 0.95, 0.92, 0.08), # Near particle attractor KnowledgeEntity("This statement is false", 0.5, 0.1, 0.9), # Near emergent attractor KnowledgeEntity("Maybe it will rain", 0.3, 0.4, 0.7), # Shadow region KnowledgeEntity("Consciousness emerges", 0.6, 0.5, 0.8) # Liminal region ] for entity in entities: classification = classifier.classify(entity) phasepoint = entity.tophasepoint() print(f"'{entity.content}' → {classification.value} at {phasepoint}") ```
